### 11.1. WCAG Compliance
- Color contrast ratios
- Keyboard navigation
- Screen reader support
- Focus management

### 11.2. Semantic HTML
- Proper heading hierarchy
- ARIA labels and roles
- Form label associations
- Alt text for images

